{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"spacePaddingBlockDensityCompactTopAlignmentTopText_container"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SpaceSemanticToken","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic05SpaceB5Tokena"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemecontrolitemcomponenttokensprovider\/spacepaddingblockdensitycompacttopalignmenttoptext_container"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"]]},"metadata":{"title":"spacePaddingBlockDensityCompactTopAlignmentTopText_container","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"spacePaddingBlockDensityCompactTopAlignmentTopText_container","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic05SpaceB5Tokena","text":"SpaceSemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B39ThemeControlItemComponentTokensProviderC043spacePaddingBlockDensityCompactTopAlignmentN14Text_containerSdvp","extendedModule":"OUDSThemesOrange","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Has for value token spaces.paddingBlockNone"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider\/spacePaddingBlockDensityCompactTopAlignmentTopText_container","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemecontrolitemcomponenttokensprovider","title":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"A class which wraps all ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for components with a "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"control item","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" layout like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSSwitch"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSRadioButton"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSCheckboItem"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllControlItemComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ControlItemComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for control-item-layout-basded components through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Such components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"borders (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),  colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")  and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"Theme Orange","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","role":"collection"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider/spacePaddingBlockDensityCompactTopAlignmentTopText_container":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemecontrolitemcomponenttokensprovider\/spacepaddingblockdensityc